entry.string: Create sample link types, links and dynamic data objects and properties. For the samples to work correctly, you must hook the Dyanamic Data module services into the Autolinks module.
entry.translation: Creete-a semple-a leenk types, leenks und dynemeec deta oobjects und pruperteees. Fur zee semples tu vurk currectly, yuoo moost huuk zee Dyunemeec Deta mudoole-a serfeeces intu zee Ootuleenks mudoole-a.

entry.string: Samples to be created are listed below. The samples will only be created where the autolink type name does not exist and the template name is not used in any existing autolink type. Delete or rename existing link types if you want to restore the samples.
entry.translation: Semples tu be-a creeted ere-a leested beloo. Zee semples veell oonly be-a creeted vhere-a zee ootuleenk type-a neme-a dues nut ixeest und zee templete-a neme-a is nut used in uny ixeesting ootuleenk type-a. Delete-a oor reneme-a ixeesting leenk types iff yuoo vunt tu resture-a zee semples. Um gesh dee bork, bork!
